phrases: Once upon a time, there was a young man with a beautiful face.
The people loved the handsome young man, but he never showed interest in loving anyone.
This was because all he loved was himself.
When the young man, who neglected to love and sought only to be loved, found someone he truly cared for,
he realized that he had lost even the words to express those feelings.
If you get excited, it will affect your health.
You still do not have the heart?
What of the young and beautiful heart?
You see, Princess Tutu interferes every time...
But Father, when he sees Princess Tutu, the old prince starts to awaken.
If you are a girl of noble raven birth, then do not whine!
Hurry up and bring me a heart!
I understand, so please calm yourself, Father!
When I think about Mytho-sama, I just feel so overcome.
Even when I am eating like this...
We have to get to our classroom soon.
You do not care about Mytho-sama anymore either, right, Ahiru?
He is changed somehow, has not he?
Or rather, do not you get the feeling he will just take any girl?
Teen idols need to be a little more approachable.
You mean they need to seem moderately stupid?
It is because he is not the real Mytho...
You are the one who returned the feeling of love to the prince, without even knowing it was dyed in the raven's blood.
Mytho must be the one suffering the most.
I want to return him to the old Mytho as soon as I can.
But how do I do that?
O young lady who has eyes of truth...
It could never hope to hold a candle to the greatness of your love.
I understand your desire to know everything about me.
But I must not fulfill that desire.
I am someone who is qualified to be a true prince, someone who loves everyone and is loved by everyone!
Right now, the ladies of this academy are consigning themselves to that man's false love!
Of my own shortcomings, must not it?
Because I just cannot give everyone enough love...
Mon cherie is a shy one.
There is no way to compare this punishment I have taken to the pain in the hearts of the many women I am hurting.
Was that guy just now a prince too?
It would be cruel to poor Father if we did not get him a sacrificial heart to eat soon.
He is never been very patient, you know.
I am sick of waiting too.
I told you, there is no Rue.
Because I get this feeling you are Rue-chan.
It does not matter what you think.
Give me your hand, s'il vous plaIt.
You do not have to be so shy, my cute one.
You bloom like a flower, you fly away like a bird.
That young lady is truly timid.
Even as they are drawn to me, it prevents them from even approaching me... this beauty!
Mademoiselle, I beg your pardon for only just now noticing your fervent gaze.
You say you are a prince?
I am someone who is qualified to be a true prince, someone who loves everyone and is loved by everyone!
I promise you that someday I will become a great enough man to accept all the love in the world.
When that happens, I am sure no one will be able to help but love me.
Despite being a crow, you have been born into an ugly human body.
And only I and the prince in the story can truly love a pitiful person like you.
You have an almost blinding pride.
It is enough to make me hate you.
Femio-sama, could not this possibly by any chance be...
The time to make a display of your charm, Femio-sama!
Now, today we will be testing your abilities.
However, there is no need to be nervous.
If you have not neglected your everyday practicing, you will have no problem.
At times like this, it seems like nothing's changed, but...
All right, first up will be Mytho-s...
I believe I am the appropriate choice to dance the first solo.
You are Femio-san from the probationary class!
Exposure to true Art should be valuable for everyone else as well.
He is really confident for someone in the probationary class.
Maybe he is really good or something?
Er, Femio-san, it is not that I do not understand your quest for Art, but learning the basics first...
Genius is misunderstood in every era.
But someday, this dance of mine...
This love of mine will satisfy the hearts of all the people.
Cat-sensei, if I were a woman, I would have MARRIED you...
There is a feeling that gets across even when it is not put into words.
A feeling that gets across even when you do not speak it...
And another rose goes to you of the intent gaze.
That is the mime for I love you!
Are they a sign of the prince's comeback?
Or are they his death cry?
I have had such a shock!
That was definitely the I love you mime, was not it?
Come to think of it, Femio gave a flower to Ahiru too, did not he?
He and Ahiru would go well together, would not they?
What is go well together zura?
We are saying that would have been better.
And here I thought Ahiru's prince had come.
Who would have thought she and the old prince would become rivals for the new prince's love?
He is just claiming to be one.
Why do not you take this chance to date Femio?
Although this prince is on a much lower level than the last one.
He and Ahiru will not get along and they will never be on the same wavelength, so it is sure to be fun!
So fun I could watch it all day and not get bored!
But it is not totally clear whether Mytho-sama's mime was really meant for Femio or not.
What if it was for ALL the girls, or something?
I think that was the real Mytho.
Because he seemed so... so sad.
His eyes showed so much pain.
It looks like you are feeling quite a bit better.
I am sorry for making you worry.
That mime was quite splendid, but it seemed so sorrowful and fragile that I am a bit concerned.
Well, rest for a little while longer.
When you feel so strongly that you would be willing to give your life, that must be when love shines most brilliantly...
But love cannot shine on that feeling alone.
You cannot marry on that feeling alone.
We are going to go capture a sacrifice, are not we?
You go back to your dorm.
I look forward to great things from you, princess.
When they say at school that Ahiru goes well together and is lovey-dovey and it is good, what do they mean zura?
Do not keep it from me zura!
Can you please be a little quieter?!
Oh, even as I speak, I go on committing more and more sins.
My beauty is such that it is enough to make even Mytho swoon, and it makes the maidens afraid to even approach me.
Deep down, they must want to sear my image into their eyes!
Yet I cannot even save those maidens from their suffering.
My heart is always open for you ladies...
To a place where we can prove our love.
Does not the atmosphere down there seem kind of dangerous?
I am sick of waiting too.
I smell blood about to be spilled!
Ahiru must really love to battle.
I am sure they went this way...
What is it you want to do, in a place like this?
No word is more unsuited to me than fear.
Well, if there were just one thing I feared...
I suppose it would be my own beauty.
If you lose your heart, you will lose that fear as well.
I hope my Father will be happy with you.
You mean you will do me the favor of introducing me to your father?
But is not this too sudden?
After all, we know far too little about each other.
What a sinful man I am!
To think I would bind your heart to me this tightly!
I can no longer fully atone through those lukewarm punishments!
Montand, it is time for THAT!
That is not what I want.
Even if it is just for one night,
I will have you assuage my father's hunger!
Tonight, I will give my all to you.
Yes, I will love only you...
Loving just one woman is something I cannot...
Please forgive me for my rudeness, mademoiselle.
I could not resist your charms.
I could not choose just one of you, something so cruel would...
For me to take THIS much of the world's love all for myself...
This is an eternal sin I can never atone for!
Jeez, nothing you are learning is good...
It is kind of like something happened and kind of did not.
Even I do not really get it...
What are you doing that for all of a sudden?!
I do not know why he did it...
But that was the real Mytho, was not it?
Are you lovey-dovey with Mytho zura?
That I would not be able to capture a sacrifice.
So it did not go well, then.
You were not loved so much that he would give his life.
The second princess is a princess who will not be loved no matter how much she confesses her own love.
Nothing goes the way you want it to, does it?!
Do you think it is possible to turn a love made impure back to normal?
I want you to stick close to Mytho as much as you can, so...
A knight who wanders around unable to do anything?
It certainly is perfect for you, Fakir.
Does it mean he will prepare a place for me to die?
Your sword is seeking blood, is not it?
All you children who love stories, come gather around.
The voice calling, come now, wake up
The brilliant light and the dew on trees are born
By the secret water's edge that no one knows of
Dance the pas de deux of life
It is a gentle, yet fierce current
How far does the labyrinth stretch?
I loved like I was dreaming
I thought how wonderful it was to be alive
I want to be there for you
Passing by even the wind and the rain clouds
